    <section id="about">
        <h2>About SpeechToken</h2>
        <p>SpeechToken (SPEECH) is a revolutionary cryptocurrency designed to protect freedom of speech by leveraging blockchain technology. Built on Binance Smart Chain (BSC), it offers decentralized governance, secure transactions, and tools to support independent creators and activists.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="features">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Low transaction fees for tipping and staking.</li>
            <li>Decentralized Autonomous Organization (DAO) governance.</li>
            <li>Deflationary tokenomics with token burning.</li>
            <li>Seamless integration with decentralized content platforms.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="tokenomics">
        <h2>Tokenomics</h2>
        <p><strong>Total Supply:</strong> 100,000,000 SPEECH</p>
        <ul>
            <li>15%: Founders/Team (3-year vesting period)</li>
            <li>30%: Liquidity and Exchanges</li>
            <li>25%: Community and Marketing</li>
            <li>20%: Staking and Rewards</li>
            <li>10%: Reserve Fund</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="roadmap">
        <h2>Roadmap</h2>
        <p><strong>Phase 1: Development</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Finalize smart contracts and conduct audits.</li>
            <li>Deploy SpeechToken on Binance Smart Chain.</li>
            <li>Launch website, whitepaper, and community channels.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Phase 2: Adoption</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Secure exchange listings on PancakeSwap and centralized exchanges.</li>
            <li>Launch airdrops, staking rewards, and marketing campaigns.</li>
            <li>Integrate with decentralized platforms.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Phase 3: Growth</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Enable DAO governance.</li>
            <li>Expand partnerships with creators and platforms.</li>
            <li>Launch a dedicated DApp for tipping and staking.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Phase 4: Maturity</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Scale to Ethereum and Solana for multi-chain support.</li>
            <li>Develop premium features like subscription services.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

